text: Cea (muhammad) midi mxng du brrda phu thi di rab swn hnung cak khamphir dxk hrux doythi phwk khea thuk cheiy chwn pi su khamphir khx ngxallxhˌ pheux khamphir nan ca di tadsin rahwang phwk khea (phwk phid praweni) læwk lum hnung nı hmu phwk khea k phinhlanghı læa phwk khea k kalang phinhlanghı xyu
